Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:37.23,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}It's been so long since we left our home behind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:43.49,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Drifting on the Milky Way almost every single day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:46.95,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where am I supposed to go ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:50.03,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}What're we really looking for ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:55.12,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Stumbling in the darkness, cold and lost
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:22:02.00,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}But a ray of hope still exists in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:07.51,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Rain or shine, always chase the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.64,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Someday, we'll fly across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:15.10,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never fearing anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:19.90,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll promise that"we'll go on ! "
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:24.07,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if you're against the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:25.57,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never stop !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:27.32,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Don't look back !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:32.74,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll one day rise above it all (never give up)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:36.58,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Who cares if the going's tough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.66,0:22:38.12,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never think !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:40.00,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Keep pushing on !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:47.09,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We can find our promised land
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:37.23,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}离乡远行 已经历漫长时光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:43.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}年年日日 漂泊在星河八荒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:46.95,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我欲去往何处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:50.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我在追寻何物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:55.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}寒冷 迷茫 在黑暗中流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:22:02.00,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但我心中仍存一线希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:07.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}无论风雨 始终追寻梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}总有一天 我们将横越苍茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:15.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}无所畏惧 展翼翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:19.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们许下誓言 绝不退让
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:24.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即便逆流而上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:25.57,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不要停下脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:27.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}切莫顾盼彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:32.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}终有一日 我们将迎来风雨后的辉煌（绝不退让）
